text: "Sweet Caroline" is a 1969 song by Neil Diamond and was released as "Sweet Caroline (Good Times Never Seemed So Good)". It went to number 3 in Australia and Canada, number 4 in the United States, number 7 in South Africa, number 8 in the United Kingdom, number 9 in Ireland and number 16 in the Netherlands. == References == Category:1969 songs Category:Neil Diamond songs Category:Bobby Womack songs Category:Andy Williams songs
title: Sweet Caroline
